viewof dwl_controls = Inputs.form({
  eps: Inputs.range([0.2, 2.5], {value: 1.0, step: 0.05, label: "Elastičnost potražnje |ε|:"}),
  tax: Inputs.range([0, 30],    {value: 15,  step: 1,    label: "Iznos poreza (t):"})
})









Prikaži kod
